Convert biomarker data table to HTML table

Source: R/bio_tab_to_html_table.R
bio_tab_to_html_table.Rd

A short description...

Usage

bio_tab_to_html_table(
  tab_for_gt,
  densities,
  cuts,
  www_path = if (dir.exists("inst/www")) {
     "inst/www"
 } else {
    
    system.file("www", package = "NpsychAssessmentTool")
 },
  print_x = FALSE
)

Arguments

tab_for_gt

A list of data.tables, where each data.table is named after the Panda table that was queried to get the data.

densities

A list of density data.

cuts

A list or data structure containing cut-off values.

www_path

Path to www/ folder that contains .css and .js files. Defaults to either inst/www or www subdir of NpsychAssessmentTool pacakge.

print_x

For debugging

Value

A shiny::tagList object representing the HTML table. Will error if tab_for_gt is not a list of data.tables as expected.
